VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?:New-Object\s+(?:System\.)?Net\.WebClient|Net\.WebClient\b)[^|;\n]*\.\s*DownloadString
WHEN EXPR MISSING:checksum|hash|signature|verify
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects WebClient.DownloadString without content verification, often used to fetch and execute remote scripts.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for WebClient DownloadString Execution.
